BatteryEMU Installer\par
\par
This installer sets up BatteryEMU (a home battery monitoring app), a local MariaDB database instance for it to use, and registers it to run automatically as either a Windows Service or a Scheduled Task.\par
\par
By clicking Install, you agree to proceed with this installation on this machine.\par
